@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_aykbic(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.07
    v1 = ((0.08 / 0.57) / tmp)
    tmp = (tmp * wp.sin((tmp + 0.03 / v1 + 0.17)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.87)) - wp.sin((v1 + 0.22 + tmp + 0.75)))
    tmp = 0.63
    data[tid] = v0
